@using InShapeModels
@model DAL.MSGType
<div id="@Enum.GetName(typeof(MessageType), Model.MessageTypeId)-tab" class="tab-pane fade @(Model.MessageTypeId == 3 ? "in active" : "")"> @*in active*@
    <form id="MessageUpdate-@Model.Id">
        @Html.AntiForgeryToken()

        <div class="form-horizontal">
            <h4>@Model.Name</h4>
            <hr />
            @Html.HiddenFor(model => model.Id)
            @Html.ValidationSummary(true, "", new { @class = "text-danger" })
            @Html.HiddenFor(model => model.MessageTypeId)
            @Html.HiddenFor(model => model.CompanyId)
            @Html.HiddenFor(model => model.Name)

            <div class="form-group">
                <label class="col-md-2 control-label">הודעת סמס: (עד 70 תווים)</label>
                <div class="col-md-10">
                    @Html.TextAreaFor(model => model.Message, 3, 50, new { htmlAttributes = new { @class = "form-control" } })
                    @Html.ValidationMessageFor(model => model.Message, "", new { @class = "text-danger" })
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="form-group">
                <label class="col-md-2 control-label">פעיל: </label>
                <div class="col-md-10">
                    @Html.CheckBoxFor(m => m.Active, new { @class = "form-control" })
                    @Html.ValidationMessageFor(model => model.Active, "", new { @class = "text-danger" })
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="form-group">
                <label class="col-md-2 control-label">
                    שליחה אוטומטית:
                </label>
                <div class="col-md-10">
                    @Html.CheckBoxFor(m => m.AutoSend, new { @class = "form-control" })
                    @Html.ValidationMessageFor(model => model.AutoSend, "", new { @class = "text-danger" })
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="form-group">
                <label class="col-md-2 control-label">
                    זמן שליחה (בדקות) :
                </label>
                <div class="col-md-10">
                    @Html.EditorFor(model => model.TimeBefore, new { htmlAttributes = new { @class = "form-control" } })
                    @Html.ValidationMessageFor(model => model.TimeBefore, "", new { @class = "text-danger" })
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="form-group">
                <div class="col-md-offset-2 col-md-10">
                    <input type="button" value="שמור" class="btn btn-default btn-primary btn-block btn_MessageUpdate" data-id="@Model.Id" />
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </form>
</div>
